:unlabeled_panel:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/filemgr.handbook
Unlabeled Floppy
  
If a floppy disk contains data in
a format the system can't recognize,
you will need to format the disk and name
it to use it.

Choose a format, name the disk, then
click on Format Disk.

Or click on Cancel & Eject to cancel the
formatting operation and eject the floppy
disk from the drive.

